{"tid":1392871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸：提醒大家，切勿因一時衝動而影響一生！","createTime":"2019-08-01T01:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:57:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a730d2800fd42f5f2a3d8275b2c7e43f4fc41a","tid":1392871,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:36:16.000Z","msg":"良民證<br />\n切勿因一時衝動而影響一生！<br />\n<br />\n有市民向我求助，因近日全家準備移居馬來西亞，但其中一孩子曾犯刑事罪，未能獲警務處發良民證而被拒移居。<br />\n<br />\n良民證的正式名稱是「無犯罪紀錄證明書」，由警務處簽發。香港人如移居它國，均需有良民證才會獲發當地居留簽證。但如有案底者，警務處不會簽發良民證「無犯罪紀錄證明書」。<br />\n<br />\n阿Ann亦愛莫能助，只能提醒大家，切勿因一時衝動而影響一生！"},{"pid":"a1ad117ac2a4c6e6adaad3e103893b7ebe94f1d2","tid":1392871,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoGB9Vb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoGB9Vb.png&h=5f91565e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcff23f6421915ecfb14b866c0d7a04c1f9e8ed6","tid":1392871,"uid":84128,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"提醒ann姐，切勿因一時愛國而影響一生！"},{"pid":"6fdbeb599e118f5fb83e89a1b0b98eed41a8296e","tid":1392871,"uid":36238,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"Ann姐提醒大家 國家無前途 要及早移民"},{"pid":"ac95438225426966c096286064cd323dbc14066c","tid":1392871,"uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"有市民向我求助，因近日全家準備移居馬來西亞，但其中一孩子曾犯刑事罪，未能獲警務處發良民證而被拒<span style=\"color: red;\">移居</span>。<br />\n重點有幾多人想移居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10494b733a69b14ee549c5bebadc192b97ddc08","tid":1392871,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dcff23f6421915ecfb14b866c0d7a04c1f9e8ed6","tid":1392871,"uid":84128,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:38:13.000Z","msg":"提醒ann姐，切勿因一時愛國而影響一生！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:41